---
layout: layouts/base.njk
numberOfLatestPostsToShow: 3
---
<main role="main" data-barba="wrapper" class="blog-content">
    <section data-barba="container">
        <h2 class="post-title-page">Hello there!</h2>
        <p class="post-links">Hey friend! Thank you for stopping by!</p>
        <div class="img-container home">
            {% image "anith-garden-c.jpeg", "Low-res dithered photo showing a stone seat in a garden" %}
        </div>
        <p>Welcome to my digital garden &mdash; feel free to explore and look around.</p>
        <p>Iâ€™m a designer exploring creativity, compassion, and emotional expression through my writing. My garden is a safe
            haven for freedom and exploration, where I thoughtfully nurture my ideas.
        </p>

        <div class="journal-index">
        {% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
        {% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
        <h3 class="page-section-header">Latest {{ latestPostsCount }} post{% if latestPostsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %}</h3>
        <div class="page-divider"></div>

        {% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
        {% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}
        {% include "postslist.njk" %}

        {% set morePosts = postsCount - numberOfLatestPostsToShow %}
        {% if morePosts > 0 %}
            <p class="post-links index">{{ morePosts }} more post{% if morePosts != 1 %}s{% endif %}
                can be found in
                <a href="/journal/">my journal</a>.</p>
        {% endif %}
        </div>
    </section>
</main>